    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. GCI of 2.3% and NIH agreement within 11.4% across all operating points provide sufficient evidence that the CFD model reliably identifies worst-case hemolysis conditions. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at all 5 flow-speed combinations. The assessment team concludes that the computational evidence, taken together with the bench validation data and the methodological grounding in the calibration study referenced in the package, supports an Accepted credibility determination for COU1.",
